com.azure.android.storage.blob.models

Class TransferInfo.Progress

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.azure.android.storage.blob.models.TransferInfo.Progress
  • Enclosing class:
    TransferInfo

    public static final class TransferInfo.Progress
extends java.lang.Object
    Type to describe progress of a transfer. When TransferInfo.getState() returns TransferInfo.State.RECEIVED_PROGRESS, calling TransferInfo.getProgress() will return an instance of this type describing current progress.
